A '''Pydyrian healing stick''' was an object made on the [[Almania]]n [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Pydyr]] with astounding healing capabilities. When rubbed against a surface, it foamed, leaving a white residue behind. It was in use all through [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] before [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] became common, and some thought it was more effective.

